{"tid":914030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數學老師想當AV女優　大奶舊照被學生搜出","createTime":"2018-11-24T01:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T02:30:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5508558c0b4f9aba0bcc1180c04d7c8299b4071","tid":914030,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"英國一名33歲中學老師阿塔維亞(Annalisa Altariva)，一張5年前拍攝的大奶舊照，被學生專業地肉搜出，事件傳開後，阿塔維亞被家長批評淫蕩，更慘遭學校停職。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，學生找到阿塔維亞的臉書，並發現她PO出許多淫蕩照片，包括有穿著爆乳性感裝、執教鞭，模仿AV淫蕩女教師的形象。阿塔維亞甚至在臉書說，自己滿腦子都是性愛，而她人生最大的「成就」，就是大家都相信她會當AV女優。事件公開後，阿塔維亞遭到學校停職，她也刪除了這些照片，但這批照片都是阿塔維亞在5年前所拍攝，仍被學生家長罵爆。<br />\n <br />\n有一名學生母親就大罵，阿塔維亞的行為已經超出尺度，「你做老師的工作，就不能有這樣子的行為，雖然人人被賦予享有私人生活的權利，但並不代表你可以肆無忌憚地炫耀，這真的很可恥」。另外還有一名學生母親就說：「說真的，現在阿塔維亞的容顏已經不如照片當時年輕，學生們看到照片都會笑，因為這些老師比我們過去的老師，要來得更有趣。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f78kSe5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff78kSe5.png&h=ce1c6611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOt1BGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOt1BGN.png&h=c3751a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1a798ae135d8d3de8b65c44471137ed48135609","tid":914030,"uid":57554,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"再睇下先，唔好意思。"},{"pid":"cb34f16890abb576a1ec1d9b92d7c98d319d7936","tid":914030,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:57:48.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦"},{"pid":"18abd2526726bbf0c79eda508de0784c50cab1ef","tid":914030,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e7960def03935e57d0993117c4812b3a09bbb4","tid":914030,"uid":66943,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/ea/c/786033/1438872256757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2Fea%2Fc%2F786033%2F1438872256757.jpg&h=dce2af7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51febcf4d8cf9650c755da1f84b80d72d72c8a5a","tid":914030,"uid":196078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當</span></span>"},{"pid":"30928bfa093ba35499aa6f3afb32ca7077795f86","tid":914030,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"當我無講過"},{"pid":"403cd0dfbdc9d2f76710a3f024ae02311d03ba56","tid":914030,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"呢d就開post 即有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28ea6c2310056b21c428fd3b388e7fda8a6834b","tid":914030,"uid":119502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"呢d一定會有圖"}]}